Title: Etheera ICO - The Future Of Real Estate with Portal + All In One Software
Body: Dear Crypto friends, I represent a successful team of ICO investment specialists who are always on the look out for ICO's of this calibre. Our team has amassed considerable knowledge and experience in the ICO sector since we formed last weekend.  My wife (Team Secretary) and my girlfriend (Treasurer) have already applied to 3 ICOs since this morning, and Im excited to tell you, that the one I had hoped for has already admitted us to the KFC stage. It's quite exclusive (by faxed invitation) so you probably won't know it by name but it's called "Prince of Nigeria coin".  Etheera Your token economics seem fair but my figures may be a little off as the numbers 7 and 11 are missing from my calculator.  Update: My wife just informed me that she has just gone 100% all in on Nigerian Prince coin. which means we have no funds remaining in the kitty and can't invest in your coin, I'm terribly sorry about that. Not to worry, my wife earns good tips as a part-time gypsy and with my girlfriend's parole hearing coming up we should be able to invest when your coin hits the exchanges. I dearly hope we can pick some up before it goes onto the moon.  More Update: I just had a meeting (by fax) with the Nigerian Prince himself, who is looking to invest in business ventures in Europe. I told him about your business model and he is very keen to get in contact. (These are the kind of benefits you get from moving in elite circles.)  Please let me know if you or your team intend to launch more ICO's, because (thanks to Prince of the Coins) it is quite likely I will be hideously wealthy and therefore in a much better position to invest.  regards  Amicus Pnd. Bcc. Pivx Coinsultant at Amicus international

Author: Etheera
Title: Etheera ICO - The Future Of Real Estate with Portal + All In One Software
Body: hy Illordic. The differences are huge as we dont just make a simple portal with property listings. We are creating a Software that contain a whole and huge Tools integrades to handle and manage all daily tasts all in one.  Please have a look into our white paper on the software feature section, there you will straight see that differneces to ususal portals or software without portal.  here some main points of the Software:  ALL IN ONE: GLOBALE PORTAL  + SOFTWARE  MATCHING: Find immediately what you are interested in and what you are looking for, no matter where in the world. Ideal for brokers with an existing customer and property portfolio. The matching allows a search query about all brokers’ network with their existing customers and search requests and wishes. International transfers and sales have never been easier.  HUGE TOOLS: Many integrated tools including CRM functions, calendars, callbacks, visits and publications, newsletter, inbox / outbox, adding external apis and services, database with owners, prospectors, project management, dashboard,  settings and access rights, import and export of datas, document creation, real estate estimates, global broker network and much more.  for more please visit www.etheera.com
